com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.boundarymatch
Class BoundaryFeatureFilter

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.boundarymatch.BoundaryFeatureFilter
public class BoundaryFeatureFilter
extends java.lang.Object

Finds features from a FeatureCollection which are within a specified distance of Features in another FeatureCollection, and vice-versa.

The filter indexes the FeatureCollections to speed up processing. It also computes the isNear relation in both directions using a spatial index on only one of the FeatureCollections. It does this by recording the relationship in both directions for each pair of near features found by iterating over one of the collections.
